subtitleNullable: Perform Text Classification in Marathi using this Dataset
descriptionNullable:
This data set contains ~12000 news article headlines which I had collected from Marathi news websites.

The data set has been cleaned and contains train and test set using which you can benchmark your classification models in Marathi

The scripts which were used to create the data set can be found [here](https://github.com/goru001/nlp-for-marathi/tree/master/datasets-preparation)
